channel.title: Julian Loves Music
channel.description: In the grand showbiz tradition of ripping off what works to make millions of his own dollars, comedian Julian McCullough (This American Life, The Tonight Show, @midnight) has taken the hugely popular DOUG LOVES MOVIES podcast and made JULIAN LOVES MUSIC. Do you love music and comedy? Does Billy Joel's music fill you with rage? You'll love JULIAN LOVES MUSIC!
